0.23a
----

- Added #@AfterInvoke with associated behaviors which now provides POSA2 interceptor before and after hooks.
- Refactored SessionScope to fix bug which occurred when an object's destructor set a new session variable and
  SessionScope already persisted.
- Added #@Stateful interceptor
- Refactored remoting component to get rid of invokeStateful since now any class can be treated as stateful
  at code time by the developer with the #@Stateful interceptor.
- Refactored #@RequestParam interceptor to support 'required' attribute
- Removed invokeStateful from remoting logic since now any class can be #@Stateful